- 'Color type not customizable' means the color cannot be changed or altered by the manufacturer post-production;
- 'Vehicle style' refers to the body style of the vehicle, such as sedan, SUV, etc.

sql:
SELECT DISTINCT color_name
FROM colors
WHERE availability = 'yes';

